<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <title>Assistante Vocale IA - Natalia automatise vos appels</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Decouvrez Natalia, l'assistante vocale IA qui repond a vos appels 24/7 avec une voix naturelle et une comprehension instantanee.">
  <%- include('./includes/_head.ejs') %>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">
<%- include('./includes/_header.ejs') %>

<main class="flex-grow">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-primary/5 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="gradient-orb gradient-orb-1"></div>
    <div class="gradient-orb gradient-orb-2"></div>
    <div class="container-content relative z-10">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h1 class="hero-title text-h1-mobile md:text-h1 font-bold text-police-titre mb-4">
            L'assistante vocale IA
            <span class="text-gradient">qui comprend vraiment</span>
            vos clients
          </h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle text-lg text-police-grey font-semibold mb-8">
            Une voix naturelle, une comprehension instantanee du langage naturel, une disponibilite 24/7 sans interruption.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-cta">
            <a href="./contact" class="btn btn-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2">
              Reserver une demo
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-image flex justify-center">
          <div class="relative animate-float-slow">
            <img src="./assets/images/businessDashboardPng.png" alt="Assistante vocale IA" class="w-full max-w-lg rounded-xl shadow-lg glow">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Differentiators Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-content">
      <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h2 font-bold text-police-titre text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        Ce qui fait la <span class="text-gradient">difference</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8" data-stagger-scale>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary text-white animate-float" style="animation-delay: 0s;">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11a7 7 0 01-7 7m0 0a7 7 0 01-7-7m7 7v4m0 0H8m4 0h4m-4-8a3 3 0 01-3-3V5a3 3 0 116 0v6a3 3 0 01-3 3z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-police-titre mb-3">Voix naturelle</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey">
            Pas de voix robotique. Natalia parle avec une voix naturelle et fluide qui met vos clients en confiance.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary to-primary text-white animate-float" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-police-titre mb-3">Comprehension IA</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey">
            Natalia comprend le langage naturel, les accents, les hesitations. Elle s'adapte a chaque interlocuteur.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary text-white animate-float" style="animation-delay: 1s;">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-police-titre mb-3">Disponible 24/7</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey">
            Pas de pause dejeuner, pas de vacances, pas de week-end. Natalia repond a chaque appel, a chaque instant.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container-content">
      <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h2 font-bold text-police-titre text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        Fonctionnalites <span class="text-gradient">avancees</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6" data-stagger-scale>
        <div class="card bg-white">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5h12M9 3v2m1.048 9.5A18.022 18.022 0 016.412 9m6.088 9h7M11 21l5-10 5 10M12.751 5C11.783 10.77 8.07 15.61 3 18.129"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Multilingue</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Francais, anglais, espagnol, allemand... Natalia s'adapte a la langue de votre interlocuteur.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-white">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-secondary/10 text-secondary">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">API & Webhooks</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Integrez Natalia a vos systemes existants via notre API REST et nos webhooks en temps reel.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-white">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Analytics</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Dashboard temps reel pour suivre les performances : taux de resolution, duree moyenne, satisfaction.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-white">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Transfert intelligent</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Natalia detecte quand un humain doit prendre le relais et transfere l'appel avec tout le contexte.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-white">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-orange-100 text-orange-600">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Securite</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Donnees chiffrees, hebergement en France, conformite RGPD. Vos conversations sont protegees.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-white">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Auto-apprentissage</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Natalia s'ameliore continuellement en apprenant de chaque conversation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How it works Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-content">
      <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h2 font-bold text-police-titre text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        Comment ca <span class="text-gradient">marche</span> ?
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8" data-stagger-scale>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary text-white text-2xl font-bold shadow-lg">
            1
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Configuration</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Nous parametrons Natalia selon vos besoins, votre vocabulaire metier et vos scenarios.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary text-white text-2xl font-bold shadow-lg">
            2
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Integration</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Natalia se connecte a votre telephonie et a vos outils metiers (CRM, ERP, ticketing...).
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary text-white text-2xl font-bold shadow-lg">
            3
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Pilote</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Nous lancons un pilote sur un perimetre defini pour valider les performances.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary text-white text-2xl font-bold shadow-lg">
            4
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Deploiement</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Une fois valide, nous deployons Natalia sur l'ensemble de vos lignes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gradient-animated text-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-white/5 rounded-full -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 animate-float"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-white/5 rounded-full translate-x-1/3 translate-y-1/3 animate-float" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
    <div class="container-content text-center relative z-10">
      <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h2 font-bold mb-6 text-white animate-on-scroll">
        Pret a decouvrir Natalia ?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-white/90 animate-on-scroll">
        Planifiez une demonstration personnalisee avec notre equipe.
      </p>
      <div class="animate-on-scroll">
        <a href="./contact" class="btn btn-white inline-flex items-center gap-2">
          Reserver une demo
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('./includes/_footer.ejs') %>

</body>
</html>
